traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/placeholdercontentview\/transaction(_:)"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"transaction"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"transform"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"inout"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV","text":"Transaction","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","text":"Void"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","text":"View","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"transform","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The transformation to apply to transactions"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"within this view."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","text":"Return Value","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A view that wraps this view and applies a transformation to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all transactions used within the view.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this modifier to change or replace the animation used in a view.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Consider three identical animations controlled by a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"button that executes all three animations simultaneously:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The first animation rotates the “Rotation” ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true},{"text":" view by 360","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"degrees.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The second uses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"transaction(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" modifier to change the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"animation by adding a delay to the start of the animation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by two seconds and then increases the rotational speed of the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"“Rotation\\nModified” ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" view animation by a factor of 2.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The third animation uses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"transaction(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" modifier to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"replace the rotation animation affecting the “Animation\\nReplaced”","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" view with a spring animation.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following code implements these animations:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["struct TransactionExample: View {","    @State private var flag = false","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 50) {","            HStack(spacing: 30) {","                Text(\"Rotation\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","","                Text(\"Rotation\\nModified\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction { view in","                        view.animation =","                            view.animation?.delay(2.0).speed(2)","                    }","","                Text(\"Animation\\nReplaced\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction { view in","                        view.animation = .interactiveSpring(","                            response: 0.60,","                            dampingFraction: 0.20,","                            blendDuration: 0.25)","                    }","            }","","            Button(\"Animate\") {","                withAnimation(.easeIn(duration: 2.0)) {","                    self.flag.toggle()","                }","            }","        }","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this modifier on leaf views such as "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Image"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button"},{"type":"text","text":" rather"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"than container views such as "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/HStack"},{"type":"text","text":". The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transformation applies to all child views within this view; calling"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"transaction(_:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" on a container view can lead to unbounded scope of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"execution depending on the depth of the view hierarchy."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/PlaceholderContentView\/transaction(_:)"},"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Button":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Button","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Button","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/button","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Button","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/VStack":{"title":"VStack","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"VStack"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A view that arranges its subviews in a vertical line."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"VStack"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/vstack"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/Image":{"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Image","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Image","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/image","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Image","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Image","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documenta